text: Baek Il-seob (; born June 10, 1944) is a South Korean actor. He is known for his roles in dramas Mom's Dead Upset, My Too Perfect Sons and Ojakgyo Brothers. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean movie actors Category:South Korean television actors Category:South Korean stage actors
